#This is the variable definition file of the exercice module `test'.
#It is part of the software wims. Author: XIAO Gang

#Each non-comment line defines a variable. Format of the line:
#
#name	allow	log	default	llim	ulim
#
#name: name of the variable
#log: log priority. 0: no log. 1: little log. 2: more log. etc.
#allow: when allow the user to override the defined value.
#       it maybe any, deny, init, config, reply.
#llim, ulim: lower and upper limits. (Not valid for string variable)
#
#
#name	allow	log	llim	ulim

status	deny	0
replycnt deny
goodcnt deny
givtype deny
asktype deny
a	deny
b	deny
c	deny
c1	deny
c2	deny
ab	deny
ba	deny
ca	deny
cb	deny
size	deny
range	deny
asklist deny
a_list	deny
b_list	deny
c_list	deny
c1_list	deny
c2_list deny
ab_list deny
ba_list deny
ca_list deny
cb_list deny
real	deny

type	init
style	init
askcnt	init
repeat  init
miss	init
good	reply

